Write the reverse method in the Edge class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class Edge {
    reverse() {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class Edge {
    reverse() {
        const temp = this.startVertex;
        this.startVertex = this.endVertex;
        this.endVertex = temp;
        if(this.curve){
           this.curve = this.curve.reverse();
        }
    }
}
```
